            . In consequence of information I apprehended the prisoner in the City-road, at the apartment of a woman of the town, on the first floor; I found there a box containing a considerable quantity of plate; the prisoner confessed to me that he had stolen that plate from the prosecutor, his uncle, and he attempted to cut his throat.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 16,</p>
               <p>Of stealing, but not in the dwelling-house.</p>
